         Drops in plane of hate off the Ashenbone Broodmaster. At least that's where I got mine. Called Encyclopedia Necrotheurgia. Looks like a book. Doesn't make sure your pet is always max summon, it's effect is to basically take what you WOULD have summoned and bump it up a level, basically adding +2 to max damage, and also strangely gives Jboot speed to the pet. And yes, it allows you to break normal maximum hit for a pet.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
